<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Access Restricted</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      color: #5a3921;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 90%;
    }
    .message {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .teacher-name {
      color: #4682b4;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .icon {
      font-size: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #4682b4;
    }
    .home-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4682b4;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .home-button:hover {
      background-color: #3a6d99;
    }
    .header {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #5a3921;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">&#128274;</div>
    <div class="header">Access Restricted</div>
    <div class="message">
      Dear <span class="teacher-name"><%= teacherName %></span>,<br>
      Sorry, you are not allowed to access this page. This page is restricted to <%=role%>.Please contact the administrator if you believe this is an error.
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="home-button">Return to Home</a>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Answer Analysis System
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 